<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="bg-[#080c14] scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy — ModelMatch</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/icon.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #f0f4ff; }
    .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #080c14; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #1e2d40; border-radius: 3px; }
    .card { background: #0f1521; border: 1px solid #1e2d40; border-radius: 8px; }
    .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #64748b; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#080c14]/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-[#1e2d40]">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer" onclick="window.location.href='/'">
        <img src="/icon.png" alt="ModelMatch" class="h-7 w-auto" />
        <div class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-white">Model</span><span class="text-[#4f7eff]">Match</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="flex-1 max-w-[680px] mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] mt-2">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">ModelMatch does not require an account or registration. We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or payment details. The only data we process is the model selection and purpose you submit for comparison, which is used solely to generate your result.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">2. Caching</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">Comparison results may be cached for up to 24 hours to improve performance. Cached results are stored anonymously and contain no personally identifiable information.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">We use Groq and HuggingFace APIs to generate comparisons. These services receive only the model identifiers and purpose description you provide. No personal data is shared.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">4. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">ModelMatch does not use tracking cookies. We do not serve ads, analytics scripts, or third-party trackers.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">Cached comparison data is automatically deleted after 24 hours. No permanent logs of your queries are maintained.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">If you have any questions about this policy, please reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#4f7eff] hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-[#1e2d40] text-center space-y-2">
    <div class="text-[11px] font-medium text-[#334155] uppercase tracking-widest">
      abdullah systems
    </div>
    <div class="text-[10px] text-[#334155]">
      © 2026 ModelMatch. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
